<{{ tool_name }}>
Execute shell commands in an isolated sandbox environment.

**Filesystem layout:**
| Path | Access | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
{% for mount in layout %}
| `{{ mount.canonical }}` | {{ mount.access }} | {{ mount.description }} |
