| `{{ skills_prefix }}*/` | ro | Mounted skill content |

Rules:
- Use absolute paths. `{{ workspace.canonical }}` is the working directory.
- Save any file the user should receive to `{{ (layout | selectattr("name", "equalto", "outputs") | first).canonical }}`.
- Do not access paths outside the directories listed above.{% if has_text_editor %}
- Prefer the text editor tools for viewing or editing existing files.{% endif %}

{% if few_shots == "True" %}
{% set uploads = layout | selectattr("name", "equalto", "uploads") | first %}
{% set outputs = layout | selectattr("name", "equalto", "outputs") | first %}
Examples:
- Read an upload: `cat {{ uploads.canonical }}report.csv`
- Install a package: `pip install pandas`
- Save result: `cp analysis.png {{ outputs.canonical }}analysis.png`
{% endif %}
